<F P=100> West Europe </F>
<H3> <TI>   Luo Gan Meets Visiting German Delegation </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Luo Gan Meets Visiting German Delegation </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW2104130694 Beijing XINHUA in English 1240 GMT 21 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW2104130694 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, April 21 (XINHUA) -- Luo Gan, Chinese State 
Councillor and secretary-general of the State Council, met with 
a delegation from Germany's Baden-Weuttemberg State here today. 
  The two sides exchanged views on the enhancement of 
bilateral 
economic cooperation. 
  The delegation, headed by the state's Minister-President 
Erwin Teufel, is here as guest of the Chinese People's Institute 
of Foreign Affairs. It is accompanied by more than 100 
entrepreneurs from Baden-Weuttemberg. 

</TEXT>

