  [Text] Shanghai, April 22 (XINHUA) -- Forty overseas 
investors from foreign-funded enterprises here were today given 
the title of "friends of Shanghai". 
  According to local officials, the idea is to give citations 
to compatriots from Hong Kong, Macao and Taiwan, overseas 
Chinese nationals, foreign managers of foreign-funded firms, 
