  He added that Egypt hopes to further enhance its ties with 
China and share the experience of China's economic reform and 
construction. 
  He voiced the hope that the two parliaments would promote 
contacts and friendship. 
  Qiao asked Mubarak to convey his greetings and an invitation 
to visit China to the Egyptian parliament's speaker, Ahmad Fathi 
Surur. 
  Mubarak also invited Qiao to visit Egypt, which Qiao 
accepted 
with pleasure. 

