<H3> <TI>   French Premier Balladur Terms Visit `Complete Success' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    French Premier Balladur Terms Visit `Complete Success' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW2204032994 Beijing XINHUA in English 0316 GMT 22 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW2204032994 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Paris, April 21 (XINHUA) -- French Prime Minister 
Edouard Balladur said here today that his recent visit to China 
was a "complete success" despite some "distorting" reports by 
certain French journalists. 
  Speaking on the Television France 1 this evening, Balladur 
stressed that China is a country with which "good relations 
should be maintained." 
  However, he added that before his visit to China earlier 
this 
