<H3> <TI>   Spokesman Reports Wang Juntao Released on Bail for Treatment </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Spokesman Reports Wang Juntao Released on Bail for Treatment </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW2304084994 Beijing XINHUA in English 0835 GMT 23 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW2304084994 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, April 23 (XINHUA) -- Wang Juntao, who had 
been in custody, has left for medical treatment abroad after the 
Chinese judicial authorities released him on bail according to 
law on account of the conditions of his illness, a spokesman for 
the Ministry of Justice said here today. 
  The spokesman was answering a question from a reporter on 
the 
release of Wang Juntao. 

