<H4>    Passes Resolution on Courts </H4>

<F P=102> OW2504133294 Hefei ANHUI RIBAO in Chinese 13 Apr 94 p 3 </F>
<F P=103> OW2504133294 </F>
<F P=104>  Hefei ANHUI RIBAO </F>
<F P=105>  Chinese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> ["Resolution of the Second Session of the Eighth Anhui </F>
Provincial People's Congress on the Work Report of the Anhui 
Provincial Higher People's Court (Adopted on 12 April 1994 at 
the Second Session of the Eighth Anhui Provincial People's 
Congress)"] 
  [Text] The Second Session of the Eighth Anhui Provincial 
People's Congress heard, examined, and deliberated over the work 
report delivered by President Han Yunping [7281 0061 5493] on 
behalf of the provincial higher people's court. The session 
decided to approve the report. 
  The session urged courts at all levels throughout the 
province to follow the guidance of Comrade Deng Xiaoping's 
theory of building socialism with Chinese characteristics as 
well as the guidelines of the 14th national party congress and 
the Third Plenary Session of the 14th CPC Central Committee; to 
uphold the guiding thought of subordinating judicial work to 
reform, development, and stability; to further strengthen 
judicial work; to continue to take stern measures against 
serious criminal offenses and economic crimes in accordance with 
the law; to actively participate in improving all facets of 
social order; to wage an in-depth anticorruption drive; to 
maintain social stability; and to protect the lawful rights and 
interests of citizens and legal persons. We should earnestly 
consolidate the ranks of people's courts, strictly enforce laws, 
and improve judicial standards so as to provide effective legal 
protection for the socialist market economic system and for 
economic construction. 

</TEXT>

